#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:1
msgid "Capabilities"
msgstr "功能特性"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"{term}`KernelGenBench` provides comprehensive capabilities for "
"{term}`Kernel` generation evaluation."
msgstr ""
"{term}`KernelGenBench` 为 {term}`内核` 生成评估提供全面的功能支持。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:5
msgid "Multi-Source Evaluation"
msgstr "多源评估"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:7
msgid "210 operators from ATen, vLLM, and cuBLAS sources."
msgstr "来自 ATen、vLLM 和 cuBLAS 来源的 210 个算子。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:9
msgid "→ See [Multi-Source Operators](../features/multi-source.md) for details."
msgstr "→ 详情请参阅[多源算子](../features/multi-source.md)。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:11
msgid "Multi-Chip Support"
msgstr "多芯片支持"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:13
msgid ""
"6 hardware platforms (NVIDIA, Ascend, MUSA, Hygon, Iluvatar, MetaX) with "
"auto-detection."
msgstr ""
"支持 6 个硬件平台（NVIDIA、Ascend、MUSA、Hygon、Iluvatar、MetaX），具备自动检测功能。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:15
msgid "→ See [Multi-Chip Support](../features/multi-chip.md) for details."
msgstr "→ 详情请参阅[多芯片支持](../features/multi-chip.md)。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:17
msgid "Two Evaluation Tracks"
msgstr "两条评估赛道"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
msgid "Track"
msgstr "赛道"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目的"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
msgid "[LLM Track](../operation-guide/llm-track/index.md)"
msgstr "[LLM 赛道](../operation-guide/llm-track/index.md)"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
#, python-brace-format
msgid "{term}`Pass@K` evaluation"
msgstr "{term}`Pass@K` 评估"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
msgid "[Agent Track](../operation-guide/agent-track/index.md)"
msgstr "[智能体赛道](../operation-guide/agent-track/index.md)"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md
msgid "Iterative generation"
msgstr "迭代生成"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:24
msgid "Anti-Hack Validation"
msgstr "防作弊验证"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:26
msgid "Three-tier mechanism (AST scan, Ghost replay, Hardware profiling)."
msgstr "三层机制（AST 扫描、Ghost 回放、硬件分析）。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:28
msgid "→ See [Anti-Hack Architecture](../features/anti-hack.md) for details."
msgstr "→ 详情请参阅[防作弊架构](../features/anti-hack.md)。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:30
msgid "Evaluation Metrics"
msgstr "评估指标"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:32
msgid "Accuracy, speedup, token cost, wall time."
msgstr "精度、加速比、Token 成本、实际运行时间。"

#: ../../source/overview/capabilities.md:34
msgid "→ See [Evaluation Metrics](../features/metrics.md) for details."
msgstr "→ 详情请参阅[评估指标](../features/metrics.md)。"
